  3.530723864064211*^9, 3.530723870045904*^9}}],

Cell["and impossible to assign finite meaning to the \"correct\"", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530723807989821*^9, 3.530723843833949*^9}}],

Cell[BoxData[
