Cell["\<\
\[LongDash]that I used to fill in the successive rows of \[EmptySquare]s in \
\[DoubleStruckCapitalM]. By this means, I construct a 20-member list of such \
connection matrices \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530642444607708*^9, 3.5306426797990103`*^9}, {
  3.530674005646762*^9, 3.530674013404203*^9}, {3.530725605284618*^9, 
  3.530725709084344*^9}}],

