Cell["\<\
\[Ellipsis]to give rise to internodal resistance matrices of only two basic \
types. The \"mean internodal resistances\" associated with those two types \
are found to be distinct.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530730406664133*^9, 3.530730466142086*^9}, {
  3.530730504594042*^9, 3.5307305494466667`*^9}}]
}, Open  ]],

