Cell["\<\
\[LongDash]one would have to forego exhaustive enumeration, would have to \
resort to some kind of fair sampling procedure. 

Here I have examined the case\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530738467156692*^9, 3.530738556605616*^9}, {
  3.530738617892847*^9, 3.530738628004377*^9}, {3.5307389605328913`*^9, 
  3.5307389610717487`*^9}}],

