Cell["\<\
The Fixed Probe Protocol requires investment in the construction of many \
m-resistor circuits. Exhaustive survey of the possibilities becomes \
impossible if n is large enough to be interesting; one must in such cases \
resort to statistical sampling. The K-R method can be used to evaluate \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530897013181014*^9, 3.530897041754694*^9}, {
  3.530897077480691*^9, 3.5308972053049717`*^9}, {3.5308974664110813`*^9, 
  3.530897479752913*^9}}],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
   SubscriptBox["R", "effective"], "[", 
   RowBox[{"a", ",", "b"}], "]"}], ":=", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "\[CapitalGamma]", "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "a", "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}],
     "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "a", "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}], "+", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "\[CapitalGamma]", "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "b", "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}],
     "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "b", "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}], "-", 
   RowBox[{"2", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{
     "\[CapitalGamma]", "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "a", 
      "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}], "\[LeftDoubleBracket]", "b", 
     "\[RightDoubleBracket]"}]}]}]}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.53089724674408*^9, 3.530897269498828*^9}}],

Cell["\<\
only if the probe nodes a & b are members of an identifiable connected \
subgraph.

The Movable Probe Protocol enables one to extract maximal data from each \
randomly constructed m-resistor circuit. The K-R method is subject to the \
same limitation as before, but it permits one to evaluate and average \
internodal resistances in subcircuit-wide batches. 

One must, in all events, identify connected subcircuits before attempting to \
exploit the K-R method. This I failed to do in \"Percolation Expereiments 1 & \
2.\" For m not too small one can expect most/all randomly constructed \
circuits to be connected,  so one can have fair confidence in the descending \
tail of the figures such as the following:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.530897299235861*^9, 3.530897356495859*^9}, {
  3.5308973892140427`*^9, 3.530897446970373*^9}, {3.530897489104192*^9, 
